
Cactus Code Thorn TriggerTerminateManual
Thorn Author(s)     : Christian D. Ott <cott@tapir.caltech.edu>
Thorn Maintainer(s) : Christian D. Ott <cott@tapir.caltech.edu>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------


Purpose of the thorn:

Watch the gone by walltime.  Trigger termination if only n minutes are
left to some limit set by the user.  Alternatively, trigger
termination if a special file with a special content exists.
